description:
This is a collection of short poems read by LibriVox volunteers for the month of September 2008.

For more information on our readers, see our catalog page: http://librivox.org/librivox-short-poetry-collection-071/

For more free audiobooks, or to become a volunteer reader, please visit librivox.org . M4B format available
